{"tid":1604392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（先知）你就係被選中嘅救世主。","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:02:29.000Z","uid":198258,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d7bf1b0cac82c692b9f049a2ab10d2aba618bbb","tid":1604392,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"發左個預知夢，見到有宇宙貓頭鷹。<br />\n<br />\n101當日，有班狗狗衝埋過黎，又有人嚇到向後跑。<br />\n但係呢個時候你好冷靜，好堅定。見到人數屌打狗狗，判斷好之後你大喝一聲：「我地夠人呀，打狗救人！」<br />\n<br />\n大家比你嘅聲音驚醒左，開始反攻。<br />\n最後你仲救得番十幾個原本比人捉住左嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n恐懼會傳染，但勇氣都係。"},{"pid":"d14797bc6974cb3f574265d550d5017191fd182f","tid":1604392,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d45c9389983c01e3695eebc65ac2708be65655c5","tid":1604392,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00e21ecff2fdc119a38db446baac4c72c9e7de1b","tid":1604392,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0883fe5145e07473b496fa173054539281550e43","tid":1604392,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:58:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ee3332ad55823d5b0d084e473c32d0afdba495d","tid":1604392,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:58:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2343bd1f2cf570315550743bc21e933544ffa1f0","tid":1604392,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:59:39.000Z","msg":"［手足入］希望大家可以多D留意屋企樓下E個位，提防D奇怪人搵有用垃圾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603671</a>"},{"pid":"0b22b7867cc7275b4bdad0784d6b99a4b56b91d3","tid":1604392,"uid":41636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"推你最底嗰句"},{"pid":"e3036800e8203e44e0a92d5ae7bb918dfc0746b7","tid":1604392,"uid":9214,"